title: ImportError: No module named '_pywrap_tensorflow'
body_html:

install python 3.5 and set the path automatically.

pip3 install --upgrade tensorflow

Note:
I have seen [https://github.com//issues/7705] and [https://github.com//issues/7529]
i also have installed Visual C++ Redistributable 2015 x64.

Thank you for any help
